overview: Last year, Hooker Stories — scenes straight from the files of real escorts — was one of Naked Sword's hottest original series. This year, we're back with more boys, and more true stories of the San Francisco flesh trade. Get out your expense accounts because these boys maybe easy, but they're certainly not cheap! Hooker Stories 2 features businessmen and tourists, spoiled brats and gay divorcees — go behind-the-scenes and find out what happens when the doors are closed and the wallets are open. It's an all-star cast led by legendary escort Diesel Washington showing you how it's done.
title: Hooker Stories 2
